Description: Hey everyone, I have a fantastic and extremely fun to play Jackson warrior 7 string Wr7 Dave Davidson of Revocation signature model. It plays like a dream and has better fret work and neck than most USA guitars I’ve had and sounds and plays incredible with really low action and zero issues. The edges have been professionally sanded (beveled) and finished to match the USA model and overall comfort of your arm resting on the edge. It feels incredibly better than the stock sharp edge it had originally and looks much better too in my opinion. Also the 3 way selector was moved to the farther location for better switching with nothing in your way. Other than that it’s in fantastic shape with zero issues or bad damage. The pearl dot stickers on the higher frets will be removed prior to shipment, or I’ll keep them on if you want them. Comes with original Dimarzio Imperium pickup set which I have also put black covers on them and they look fantastic, backplate and truss rod covers (will be put back on prior to shipment), and original Floyd rose trem arm (not the cheaper trem arm it comes with standard). NO case, but will be double boxed and packed like it’s going to war. If you have any questions please feel free to message me at any time. I have 100% feedback in sales on here, Reverb, and tons of forums and exchanges so bid with confidence! Will ship same day or next day depending on when payment is received. Thanks for looking and god bless.
Title: Jackson Wr7 Warrior 7 String Dave Davidson Sig w/ Dimarzios + Floyd Rose!
